</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0755A263FFCBFF81A7ADF890FCACDBE9" blockId="82.[189,1399,1919,2025]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFCBFF81A7ADF890FDE9DB98" author="Torres-Contreras R. A. &amp; Arroyo-Perez W. &amp; Alvarez-Garcia D. M." box="[189,559,1919,1945]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Torres-Contreras" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" pagination="129 - 141" part="4664" refId="ref154819" refString="Torres-Contreras R. A., Arroyo-Perez W. &amp; Alvarez-Garcia D. M. 2019. Charinus rocamadre (Amblypygi, Charinidae): Description of the female, ultrastructure of the male and female gonopods, and mitochondrial DNA sequences. Zootaxa 4664: 129 - 141. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4664.1.6" title="Charinus rocamadre (Amblypygi, Charinidae): Description of the female, ultrastructure of the male and female gonopods, and mitochondrial DNA sequences" type="journal article" year="2019">
Torres-Contreras 
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFCBFF81A681F86FFE15DB98" box="[401,467,1919,1945]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">et al.</emphasis>
(2019)
</bibRefCitation>
described the female of 
<taxonomicName id="C0EAD9E0FFCBFF81A463F86FFBDDDB98" authorityName="Torres-Contreras et al." authorityYear="2015" box="[883,1051,1919,1946]" class="Arachnida" family="Charinidae" genus="Charinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amblypygi" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rocamadre">
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFCBFF81A463F86FFBDDDB98" box="[883,1051,1919,1946]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">C. rocamadre</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, provided additional details concerning the male gonopod, and published a DNA barcode of the species. See 
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFCBFF81A37EF848FECDDBE8" author="Torres-Contreras R. &amp; Garcia D. M. A. &amp; Armas L. F." etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Torres-Contreras" journalOrPublisher="Revista Iberica de Aracnologia" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" pagination="145 - 148" part="27" refId="ref154773" refString="Torres-Contreras R., Garcia D. M. A. &amp; Armas L. F. 2015. Una especie nueva de Charinus Simon, 1892 (Amblypygi: Charinidae) del Caribe Colombiano. Revista Iberica de Aracnologia 27: 145 - 148." title="Una especie nueva de Charinus Simon, 1892 (Amblypygi: Charinidae) del Caribe Colombiano" type="journal article" year="2015">
Torres-Contreras 
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFCBFF81A22CF847FAB1DBC0" box="[1340,1399,1959,1985]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">et al.</emphasis>
(2015)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="637BDF92FFCBFF81A654F821FD67DBE9" author="Torres-Contreras R. A. &amp; Arroyo-Perez W. &amp; Alvarez-Garcia D. M." box="[324,673,1998,2024]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Torres-Contreras" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" pagination="129 - 141" part="4664" refId="ref154819" refString="Torres-Contreras R. A., Arroyo-Perez W. &amp; Alvarez-Garcia D. M. 2019. Charinus rocamadre (Amblypygi, Charinidae): Description of the female, ultrastructure of the male and female gonopods, and mitochondrial DNA sequences. Zootaxa 4664: 129 - 141. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4664.1.6" title="Charinus rocamadre (Amblypygi, Charinidae): Description of the female, ultrastructure of the male and female gonopods, and mitochondrial DNA sequences" type="journal article" year="2019">
Torres-Contreras 
<emphasis id="359E7E71FFCBFF81A501F820FD8ADBE9" box="[529,588,1998,2024]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">et al.</emphasis>
(2019)
</bibRefCitation>
for more details.
</paragraph>
